Everything that we directly measure

3120
02:01:22,350 --> 02:01:24,250
takes place at the bottom.

3121
02:01:24,530 --> 02:01:29,750
Including the microwave background.

3122
02:01:30,830 --> 02:01:32,740
The microwave background originated

3123
02:01:32,740 --> 02:01:34,650
a couple hundred years ago.

3124
02:01:34,670 --> 02:01:36,320
500,000 years after we fell off

3125
02:01:36,320 --> 02:01:37,970
the top of the edge there.

3126
