The universe cooled a lot.

3127
02:01:40,910 --> 02:01:43,070
When it fell off the top of that edge there,

3128
02:01:43,210 --> 02:01:45,840
the scales involved were hugely

3129
02:01:45,840 --> 02:01:48,470
hot temperatures by our normal standard.

3130
02:01:48,990 --> 02:01:51,000
The universe had to cool a great

3131
02:01:51,000 --> 02:01:53,010
deal before it cooled down to the point

3132
02:01:53,610 --> 02:01:57,230
where the recombination or the

3133
