Roughly 200,000 years.

3139
02:02:10,550 --> 02:02:13,170
So it's almost all the way back to the beginning.

3140
02:02:13,870 --> 02:02:15,870
200,000 years is a very short,

3141
02:02:15,870 --> 02:02:17,230
fractional time.

3142
02:02:17,510 --> 02:02:18,070
Right.

3143
02:02:19,530 --> 02:02:20,090
