3164
02:03:12,330 --> 02:03:14,490
So that's a separate...

3165
02:03:14,490 --> 02:03:15,970
My understanding is that people

3166
02:03:15,970 --> 02:03:17,450
who do the statistics of it

3167
02:03:17,450 --> 02:03:20,610
don't think it's a statistically significant thing.

3168
02:03:23,009 --> 02:03:24,589
I don't have a strong opinion

3169
02:03:24,589 --> 02:03:26,170
about it one way or another.

3170
02:03:26,390 --> 02:03:27,510
The problem is,

3171
02:03:27,510 --> 02:03:28,830
with the universe,

3172
02:03:28,830 --> 02:03:30,770
you can't really...

3173
02:03:30,770 --> 02:03:33,350
Certain things you can do statistics with,

3174
02:03:33,350 --> 02:03:34,530
and certain things you can't.

3175
02:03:34,630 --> 02:03:35,990
For example,

3176
02:03:35,990 --> 02:03:39,830
