3177
02:03:40,530 --> 02:03:43,350
There are small-scale variations.

3178
02:03:43,550 --> 02:03:45,250
Let's say small-scale variations involving

3179
02:03:45,250 --> 02:03:46,950
a tenth of a degree.

3180
02:03:47,650 --> 02:03:49,880
There are many small-scale variations

3181
02:03:49,880 --> 02:03:52,110
involving a tenth of a degree.

3182
02:03:53,750 --> 02:03:55,930
You can do some statistics on them,

3183
02:03:56,520 --> 02:04:01,670
and you can ask whether the small-scale variations like this

3184
02:04:01,670 --> 02:04:04,350
are isotropically distributed,

3185
02:04:04,630 --> 02:04:05,550
it makes sense to ask,

3186
02:04:05,550 --> 02:04:06,480
and you can do it

3187
02:04:06,480 --> 02:04:07,410
because you have many of them.

3188
02:04:08,350 --> 02:04:09,330
On the other hand,

3189
02:04:09,330 --> 02:04:12,210
